<db:abstract>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qwintaskbarprogress.xml">QWinTaskbarProgress</db:link> class represents a progress indicator in the Windows taskbar.</db:para>
<db:para>This class was introduced in Qt 5.2.</db:para>
