<db:section xml:id="paused-prop">
<db:title>paused : bool</db:title>
<db:para>This property holds whether the progress indicator is paused.</db:para>
<db:para>The default value is <db:code>false</db:code>.</db:para>
<db:para>The final appearance of a paused progress indicator depends on the active Windows theme. Typically, a paused progress indicator turns yellow to indicate that the progress is currently paused. Unlike a <db:link xlink:href="qwintaskbarprogress.xml#stopped-prop">stopped</db:link> progress indicator, a paused progress should not be used to indicate an error.</db:para>
